{"name":"Wallabag ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ","nodes":[{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"wallabag-search","responseMode":"lastNode","options":{}},"id":"webhook-trigger","name":"Webhook","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":2.1,"position":[240,400]},{"parameters":{"jsCode":"const keyword = $json.body.keyword || "";
const tag = $json.body.tag || "";
const days = $json.body.days || "";

let apiUrl = "https://wallabag.meowlove.cn/api/entries.json";
let params = [];

if (tag) {
  params.push("tags=" + tag);
}

if (keyword) {
  params.push("search=" + keyword);
}

if (days) {
  const since = new Date();
  since.setDate(since.getDate() - parseInt(days));
  params.push("since=" + since.toISOString());
}

return {
  url: apiUrl + (params.length > 0 ? "?" + params.join("&") : ""),
  keyword: keyword,
  tag: tag,
  days: days
};","options":{}},"id":"build-query","name":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ—Ø","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[460,400]},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"={{ $json.url }}","authentication":"genericCredentialType","genericAuthType":"httpHeaderAuth","options":{}},"id":"http-request","name":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩWallabag API","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.3,"position":[680,400]},{"parameters":{"jsCode":"const entries = $json._embedded.items || [];

if (entries.length === 0) {
  return {
    message: "√ªÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ“µÔøΩ∆•ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ",
    results: []
  };
}

const results = entries.map((entry, index) => {
  return {
    id: entry.id,
    title: entry.title,
    url: entry.url,
    tags: entry.tags.join(", "),
    created_at: entry.created_at,
    reading_time: entry.reading_time
  };
});

return {
  message: `ÔøΩ“µÔøΩ ${results.length} ∆™ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ`,
  results: results
};","options":{}},"id":"format-results","name":"ÔøΩÔøΩ ΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[900,400]},{"parameters":{"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{}},"id":"respond-webhook","name":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÿΩÔøΩÔøΩ","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","typeVersion":1.5,"position":[1120,400]}],"connections":{"Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ—Ø","type":"main","index":0}]]},"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ—Ø":{"main":[[{"node":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩWallabag API","type":"main","index":0}]]},"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩWallabag API":{"main":[[{"node":"ÔøΩÔøΩ ΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ","type":"main","index":0}]]},"ÔøΩÔøΩ ΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩ":{"main":[[{"node":"ÔøΩÔøΩÔøΩÿΩÔøΩÔøΩ","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1","callerPolicy":"workflowsFromSameOwner","availableInMCP":false},"active":false,"versionId":"cb17b628-6d23-4bbf-a6c8-0eae68daafe0","id":"7hAp2Q8s15HGtdx5","description":null,"staticData":null,"meta":null,"pinData":null,"activeVersionId":null,"updatedAt":"2026-02-05T17:53:51.773Z","createdAt":"2026-02-05T17:53:51.773Z","isArchived":false,"versionCounter":1,"triggerCount":0}

